# Component Structure

Organize components into:

components/

layout/

sections/

ui/

## UI Components

Should contain:

Buttons

Inputs

Cards

Badges

Chips

Icons

Reusable UI only.

## Sections

Large page sections.

Example:

Hero

About

Membership

Testimonials

FAQ

Contact

Footer

## Layout

Navbar

Footer

Container

Wrapper

Navigation

## Rules

Never duplicate components.

Reuse existing components whenever possible.